
# Golden Test Cases

---

# TC-01 Checkout

## Requirement

As a customer,
I want to checkout,
so I can purchase products.

---

Customer Problem

Customer cannot complete purchases.

---

Customer Value

Customer successfully buys a product.

---

Hypothesis

If customers can complete checkout easily,
conversion rate will increase.

---

Recommended Vertical Slice

- One product
- One address
- One payment method

---

SPIDR Pattern

Workflow

Reason

Checkout is a sequential process.

---

INVEST Review

Independent : ⚠️

Negotiable : ✅

Valuable : ✅

Estimable : ⚠️

Small : ❌

Testable : ⚠️

